# pve-mod :: node_info patch manifest
# Format: <patch-file> [section.key=value]
# Patches are applied top-to-bottom. An optional condition (read from this mod's
# conf.d file, /etc/pve-mod/conf.d/node_info.conf) gates a patch; it is applied
# only when the key equals the given value.

01-nodes-pm-sensors.patch
02-nodes-pm-GPU-RRD-history.patch    gpu.gpu_history=1
03-pvemanager-js-sensors.patch
